    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get there's two sides, but some people say it's really just about power. Like, doesn't it seem like when unions get too strong, they stop actually helping workers and just end up hurting the whole economy by creating these huge inefficiencies? is there a point where they become more of a problem than a solution?",
